data.description:
Unwind in this stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home located at 830 Solomon Drive in Jacksonville. This spacious property is perfect for families or anyone looking for a comfortable and welcoming living space. There is plenty of room for everyone to spread out and relax. The open floor plan and windows flood the home with natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The stylish kitchen features sleek appliances and ample counter space, making meal prep a breeze. Outside, the fenced backyard offers privacy for outdoor entertaining and play. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is just a short drive from shopping, dining, and entertainment options and all military bases. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful property your next home.

Pet Negotiable. Age, weight and breed restrictions apply. No more than 2 pets allowed. One time non-refundable pet fee applies per pet. Atleast one applicant must apply with pet screening on the online application whether you have a pet or not. 

Renters Insurance required prior to move in. Security Deposit and $300 Cleaning Fee required.

Smoking allowed:No
